00:52:52.065 --> 00:52:58.237 line:90% position:50% align:center
You’re always looking out
to help behind the scenes

00:52:58.237 --> 00:53:05.411 line:90% position:50% align:center
Without the hope of praise
for all you do for those in need.

00:53:05.411 --> 00:53:12.043 line:90% position:50% align:center
The gifts you give in secret
have become known.

00:53:12.043 --> 00:53:19.968 line:90% position:50% align:center
You’ve lifted others up
