00:53:19.968 --> 00:53:26.683 line:90% position:50% align:center
You think it’s not much,
but there are so many times

00:53:26.683 --> 00:53:29.602 line:90% position:50% align:center
You have touched our lives.

00:53:32.021 --> 00:53:39.153 line:90% position:50% align:center
We see you, sister,
Always a smile on your face.

00:53:39.153 --> 00:53:45.743 line:90% position:50% align:center
You keep on going
Though you may doubt your precious place.

