If you could only see yourself
through our eyes,

00:53:52.417 --> 00:53:59.882 line:90% position:50% align:center
Then you would know how we see you.
We see you, sister.

00:54:09.017 --> 00:54:15.565 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah’s greater
than your heart.

00:54:15.565 --> 00:54:22.196 line:90% position:50% align:center
He sees the beautiful gem
that you are

00:54:22.196 --> 00:54:26.743 line:90% position:50% align:center
As you work hard
to do your part.

